data.description: You'll love this 3-bedroom property in the esteemed Community of The Bridges! It flaunts a verdant landscape, a 2-car garage, a paver driveway, & a private courtyard. Inviting hallway ushers you to the captivating open floor layout adorned w/high ceilings, tile flooring, recessed lighting, & neutral palette that exudes elegance. The chef's kitchen is fully equipped w/a gas cooktop, wall oven, & granite counters. Handsome wood cabinetry w/crown molding, a walk-in pantry, tile backsplash, & two islands, one w/a breakfast bar, elevate the space. French doors open to a practical den ideal for a home office! The grand main suite highlights a wood-style floor, a private bathroom w/dual sinks, a step-in shower, & a sitting area w/a bay window. Escape to the backyard paradise that invites you to relax & have fun! It boasts a covered patio, a well-manicured landscape, a firepit, & a crystal blue pool ready to enjoy. This gem won't disappoint!
